<h1>ChamboulDé!<sup>&copy;</sup></h1>

<div>

    <h2>RULES</h2>
    <p>Each player takes his turn throwing the dice and counts the number of points obtained.</p>
    <p>The first one who reaches 100 points or more wins the game!</p>

    <ul>
        <li>1 pair = 1 point</li>
        <li>2 pairs = 6 points</li>
        <li>3 alike = 3 points</li>
        <li>4 alike = 8 points</li>
        <li>5 alike = 20 points</li>
        <li>1 pair & 3 alike = 10 points</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Have fun!</p>

</div>

